Package jdk.test.lib.hotspot.ir_framework

Annotation Interface DontInline

@Retention(RUNTIME) public @interface DontInline
Prevent an inlining of the annotated helper method (not specifying @Test, @Check, or @Run). Non-helper methods are never inlined. Explicitly using this annotation on non-helper methods results in a TestFormatException.
